<a name="311"><span style="display: none">Exhibitor Staff Guide is Now Available</span></a>
<br>

<div class="sub-content-header">Exhibitor Staff Guide is Now Available</div><br/>

<p><img align="right" alt="" border="2" src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/newsletter/2012Exhibitor_StaffGuide.jpeg" style="padding:5px;margin-left: 5px;" />Are you putting together a 2012 International CES on-site staff guide for your company? If so, we just made it a lot easier for you to create a guide for your colleagues to use on-site. Choose from an array of helpful documents &ndash; from badge holder pickup information to a list of suggested restaurants &ndash; or simply print out a complete staff guide that we have put together for you. You may want to include a personalized cover, your booth number and company contact information. Otherwise, we have taken care of the rest for you!&nbsp;</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<a name="310"><span style="display: none">Be on the Look Out For Your Space Selection Packets</span></a>
<br>

<div class="sub-content-header">Be on the Look Out For Your Space Selection Packets</div><br/>

<p><div>
	Be on the lookout in mid-December for your 2013 International CES space selection packets. These packets will be mailed to you and will include your scheduled space selection date, time and space selection number as well as web links to other space selection information such as floor plans.</div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	As a current CES exhibitor, you already know why CES is an important investment for your company. Next year&#39;s show in 2013 is no exception! If you want to boost your brand awareness, increase your ROI and connect with C-level decision makers, don&rsquo;t miss this great opportunity to select your space for 2013. We&rsquo;ll see you in 2012, and have a great show!&nbsp;</div>
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<a name="309"><span style="display: none">Announce Celebrity Appearances and Special Events</span></a>
<br>

<div class="sub-content-header">Announce Celebrity Appearances and Special Events</div><br/>

<p><img align="right" alt="" border="2" src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/newsletter/LadyGaga_Polaroid.jpeg" style="padding:5px;margin-left: 5px;" />Is your company planning a special concert with a popular chart-topper? How about an autograph session with Hollywood royalty or a product demonstration with a sports legend? If so, let us know! We can assist you with special security arrangements, staging requirements, catering requests or anything else you need to make your event a success. We&rsquo;ll help you publicize it by including details on CESweb.org, in news releases and in the press room. Many exhibitors that host special events or celebrities choose not to announce their events until closer to the show and we will certainly accommodate those requests. We will also be happy to designate it as strictly invitation-only. Download this form to submit.&nbsp;</p>
<br>

